Name: ALPAGES : THE FIVE BOOKS
About the game: You may like : / THE GAME: You are the last guardian of the five books. Whenever they appear somewhere in the world, you must find them and survive the creatures of each book. The fifth book will give you the power to kill the witch and this will put an end to these horrors.Each time you collect a book you unleash another freaky supernatural being into the game. RUN,ESCAPE,SHOOT,SURVIVE AND FIND THE 5 BOOKS ! CONTROLS: The game controls are Classical FPS shooter. MOBS: ZOMBIES and INFECTED ANIMALS are very aggressive, THE WITCH will do everything to stop you. she loves dangerous dogs.She is the big boss off others ,THE PSYCHO-CLOWN love taking time to kill its prey and chase incessantly, THE TEDDY BEAR has two faces, THE PLANT would see the world made of trees and plants.
